  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user|, I don't want to be distracted especially when I use the app for the very first time, so I have a good user experience\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: We need to improve Opt Metrics screen appearance which is shown after I create or recover the account. It is shown after ~1 second after I create an account (not each time but in some cases) and ~2 seconds when I recover it (it happens more often) so I see the Home screen for a while and then this screen appears. I find it personally a bit distracting.  We need to show this screen right after the user is logged (for new or recovered account) so he won't see the Home screen before.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nOpt Metrics screen is shown right after login (for new and recovered account flows)\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nHome tab is shown for a second and then Opt Metrics screen pops up and distracts me\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Create account\r\n- Recover account\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: develop\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS",
